The following example demonstrates how to set the name of the folder from archive that should be rendered.

ViewerHtmlHandler htmlHandler = new ViewerHtmlHandler();
HtmlOptions options = new HtmlOptions();
options.ArchiveOptions.FolderName = "FolderName";

string guid = "archive.zip";
List<PageHtml> pages = htmlHandler.GetPages(guid, options);

The following example demonstrates how to set the maximum number of message to be rendered from outlook data files.

